#: get-started/index.md:block 8 (paragraph)
msgid "Find client libraries, example apps, and open source projects in your preferred coding languages."
msgstr "Aimsigh leabharlanna cliant, aipeanna samplacha, agus tionscadail foinse oscailte i do theangacha códaithe is fearr leat."

#: get-started/browse-languages.md:meta.title
#: get-started/browse-languages.md:title
msgid "Browse by programming language"
msgstr "Brabhsáil de réir teanga ríomhchlárúcháin"

#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "API client libraries by language"
msgstr "Leabharlanna cliant API de réir teanga"

#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 4 (header)
msgid "Open source projects by language"
msgstr "Tionscadail foinse oscailte de réir teanga"

#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 5 (paragraph)
msgid "Find Wikimedia open source projects by programming language, and start contributing code."
msgstr "Aimsigh tionscadail foinse oscailte Wikimedia de réir teanga ríomhchlárúcháin, agus tosaigh ag cur cód leis."

#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 6 (paragraph)
msgid "[Browse projects](../contribute/by-language.md){ .md-button }"
msgstr "[Brabhsáil tionscadail](../contribute/by-language.md){ .md-button }"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:meta.title get-started/new-dev.md:title
#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Understand the development process"
msgstr "Tuig an próiseas forbartha"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 2 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to make technical contributions to Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Foghlaim conas ranníocaíochtaí teicniúla a dhéanamh le tionscadail Wikimedia."

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Find tickets, and track projects"
msgstr "Aimsigh ticéid, agus rianaigh tionscadail"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikimedia uses Phabricator for task management and bug reporting. To interact with tasks, create a Phabricator account."
msgstr "Úsáideann Wikimedia Phabricator le haghaidh bainistíocht tascanna agus tuairisciú fabhtanna. Chun idirghníomhú le tascanna, cruthaigh cuntas Phabricator."

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit Phabricator](https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/)"
msgstr "[Tabhair cuairt ar Phabricator](https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/)"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Phabricator/Help)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Phabricator/Help)"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 15 (header)
msgid "Learn how to submit code"
msgstr "Foghlaim conas cód a chur isteach"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 16 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikimedia uses Gerrit and GitLab for code review. Before you submit code, get familiar with the tools, processes, and best practices."
msgstr "Úsáideann Wikimedia Gerrit agus GitLab le haghaidh athbhreithniú cóid. Sula gcuireann tú cód isteach, bíodh eolas agat ar na huirlisí, na próisis agus na dea-chleachtais."

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more about Gerrit](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Gerrit/Tutorial)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh faoi Gerrit](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Gerrit/Tutorial)"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more about GitLab](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/GitLab)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh faoi GitLab](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/GitLab)"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 2 (header)
msgid "Tutorials for using content and data"
msgstr "Ranganna teagaisc maidir le húsáid ábhair agus sonraí"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 3 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn the basics of using Wikimedia content and data in your project."
msgstr "Foghlaim bunghnéithe úsáid ábhar agus sonraí Wikimedia i do thionscadal."

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "[Browse tutorials](../use-content/tutorials.md){ .md-button }"
msgstr "[Brabhsáil ranganna teagaisc](../use-content/tutorials.md){ .md-button }"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 5 (header)
msgid "Tutorials for building tools and bots"
msgstr "Ranganna teagaisc chun uirlisí agus botanna a thógáil"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 6 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn the basics of writing code that interacts with Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Foghlaim bunghnéithe scríobh cóid a idirghníomhaíonn le tionscadail Wikimedia."

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "[Browse tutorials](../build-tools/tutorials.md){ .md-button }"
msgstr "[Brabhsáil ranganna teagaisc](../build-tools/tutorials.md){ .md-button }"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:meta.title
#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:title get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 1
#: (header)
msgid "Learn about Wikimedia technology"
msgstr "Foghlaim faoi theicneolaíocht Wikimedia"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 2 (paragraph)
msgid "Explore core Wikimedia technology and open source projects."
msgstr "Déan iniúchadh ar phríomhtheicneolaíocht Wikimedia agus ar thionscadail foinse oscailte."

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "Introduction to Wikimedia technology"
msgstr "Réamhrá ar theicneolaíocht Wikimedia"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn about the main technical areas where developers can contribute."
msgstr "Foghlaim faoi na príomhréimsí teicniúla inar féidir le forbróirí cur leis."

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/New_Developers/Introduction_to_the_Wikimedia_Technical_Ecosystem)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/New_Developers/Introduction_to_the_Wikimedia_Technical_Ecosystem)"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 21 (header)
msgid "Wikibase and Wikidata"
msgstr "Wikibase agus Wikidata"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 22 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikibase is a MediaWiki extension for working with structured data, and it's the software that powers Wikidata."
msgstr "Is síneadh MediaWiki é Wikibase le haghaidh oibriú le sonraí struchtúrtha, agus is é an bogearra a chumhachtaíonn Wikidata."

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 23 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit wikidata.org](https://www.wikidata.org/)"
msgstr "[Tabhair cuairt ar wikidata.org]( https://www.wikidata.org/)"

#: get-started/wikimedia-tech.md:block 23 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikibase)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org]( https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikibase)"

#: use-content/index.md:block 2 (header)
msgid "[Explore featured apps](featured-apps.md)"
msgstr "[Iniúchadh a dhéanamh ar aipeanna le feiceáil](featured-apps.md)"

#: use-content/index.md:block 3 (paragraph) use-content/featured-apps.md:block
#: 2 (paragraph)
msgid "See examples of open source apps and data visualizations built with Wikimedia content and data."
msgstr "Féach samplaí d’aipeanna foinse oscailte agus d’amharcléirithe sonraí atá tógtha le hábhar agus sonraí Wikimedia."

#: use-content/index.md:block 5 (paragraph) use-content/tutorials.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Follow step-by-step guides to learn the basics of using Wikimedia content and data."
msgstr "Lean treoracha céim ar chéim chun foghlaim faoi bhunús úsáid ábhar agus sonraí Wikimedia."

#: use-content/index.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "[Use wiki content](content.md)"
msgstr "[Úsáid ábhar vicí](content.md)"

#: use-content/index.md:block 7 (paragraph) use-content/content.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Find open source libraries, get started using the API, or download content in bulk."
msgstr "Aimsigh leabharlanna foinse oscailte, tosaigh ag baint úsáide as an API, nó íoslódáil ábhar i mórchóir."

#: use-content/index.md:block 8 (header)
msgid "[Access open data](data.md)"
msgstr "[Rochtain ar shonraí oscailte](data.md)"

#: use-content/index.md:block 9 (paragraph) use-content/data.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Explore public data that you can use in research and machine learning."
msgstr "Déan iniúchadh ar shonraí poiblí ar féidir leat a úsáid i dtaighde agus i bhfoghlaim meaisín."

#: use-content/index.md:block 10 (header)
msgid "[High-volume and commercial access](bot-traffic.md)"
msgstr "[Rochtain ardtoirte agus tráchtála](bot-traffic.md)"

#: use-content/index.md:block 11 (paragraph)
msgid "Review policies and options for sustainable access to Wikimedia infrastructure."
msgstr "Athbhreithniú a dhéanamh ar bheartais agus roghanna maidir le rochtain inbhuanaithe ar bhonneagar Wikimedia."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:meta.title use-content/bot-traffic.md:title
#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "High-volume and commercial access"
msgstr "Rochtain ardtoirte agus tráchtála"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 2 (paragraph)
msgid "High-volume, commercial, and bot access to Wikimedia infrastructure must comply with the following policies to avoid harming Wikipedia and other Wikimedia projects. To prevent your access from being restricted, ensure that you follow these policies."
msgstr "Caithfidh rochtain ardtoirte, tráchtála agus bota ar bhonneagar Wikimedia cloí leis na beartais seo a leanas chun dochar a sheachaint do Vicipéid agus do thionscadail Wikimedia eile. Chun cosc ​​a chur ar do rochtain a bheith srianta, déan cinnte go leanann tú na beartais seo."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "Review the terms of use"
msgstr "Athbhreithnigh na téarmaí úsáide"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn about the services that the Wikimedia Foundation provides and how you can comply with the terms of use."
msgstr "Foghlaim faoi na seirbhísí a sholáthraíonn Fondúireacht Wikimedia agus conas is féidir leat cloí leis na téarmaí úsáide."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on the Wikimedia Foundation Governance Wiki](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Terms_of_Use)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Vicí Rialachais Fhondúireacht Wikimedia](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Terms_of_Use)"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Review the API policy"
msgstr "Athbhreithnigh an polasaí API"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to use Wikimedia APIs responsibly and prevent access restrictions."
msgstr "Foghlaim conas APIanna Wikimedia a úsáid go freagrach agus srianta rochtana a sheachaint."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on the Wikimedia Foundation Governance Wiki](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Wikimedia_Foundation_API_Usage_Guidelines)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Vicí Rialachais Fhondúireacht Wikimedia](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Wikimedia_Foundation_API_Usage_Guidelines)"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 9 (header) use-content/content.md:block 18
#: (header)
msgid "Get services for enterprise"
msgstr "Faigh seirbhísí do ghnólachtaí"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 10 (paragraph)
#: use-content/content.md:block 19 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikimedia Enterprise provides a suite of APIs and services designed for high-volume, commercial access to Wikimedia content and data."
msgstr "Cuireann Wikimedia Enterprise sraith APIanna agus seirbhísí ar fáil atá deartha le haghaidh rochtain tráchtála ardtoirte ar ábhar agus sonraí Wikimedia."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 11 (unordered list)
#: use-content/content.md:block 20 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikimedia Enterprise](https://enterprise.wikimedia.com/?utm_source=wmfdev)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Wikimedia Enterprise](https://enterprise.wikimedia.com/?utm_source=wmfdev)"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 12 (header)
msgid "Partner with us"
msgstr "Comhpháirtíocht linn"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 13 (paragraph)
msgid "Contact the Wikimedia Foundation to explore options for technical partnerships."
msgstr "Téigh i dteagmháil le Fondúireacht Wikimedia chun roghanna maidir le comhpháirtíochtaí teicniúla a iniúchadh."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 14 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Technical_partnerships)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Technical_partnerships)"

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 16 (paragraph)
msgid "Ask questions about bot traffic and high-volume access."
msgstr "Cuir ceisteanna faoi thrácht bot agus rochtain ardtoirte."

#: use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Bot_traffic)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Bot_traffic)"

#: use-content/content.md:meta.title use-content/content.md:title
#: use-content/content.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Use wiki content"
msgstr "Úsáid ábhar vicí"

#: use-content/content.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "Introduction to Wikimedia projects"
msgstr "Réamhrá do thionscadail Wikimedia"

#: use-content/content.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikimedia content is organized by project and language. Each project hosts a different type of free content, like encyclopedia articles on Wikipedia, media files on Wikimedia Commons, and structured data on Wikidata."
msgstr "Eagraítear ábhar Wikimedia de réir tionscadail agus teanga. Bíonn cineál difriúil ábhair shaor in aisce i ngach tionscadal, amhail ailt chiclipéide ar Vicipéid, comhaid meán ar Wikimedia Commons, agus sonraí struchtúrtha ar Wikidata."

#: use-content/content.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikimedia_projects)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Meta-Wiki]( https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikimedia_projects)"

#: use-content/content.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Review the terms and conditions"
msgstr "Athbhreithnigh na téarmaí agus coinníollacha"

#: use-content/content.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Most Wikimedia content is licensed under a Creative Commons license that allows free reuse with attribution. You can check the bottom of any wiki page to find the applicable license."
msgstr "Tá ceadúnas Creative Commons ag formhór ábhar Wikimedia a cheadaíonn athúsáid saor in aisce le haitheantas. Is féidir leat bun aon leathanaigh vicí a sheiceáil chun an ceadúnas is infheidhme a fháil."

#: use-content/content.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on the Wikimedia Foundation Governance Wiki](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Legal:Developer_app_guidelines)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Vicí Rialachais Fhondúireacht Wikimedia](https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Legal:Developer_app_guidelines)"

#: use-content/data.md:meta.title use-content/data.md:title
#: use-content/data.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Access open data"
msgstr "Rochtain ar shonraí oscailte"

#: use-content/data.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "Use Wikimedia open data"
msgstr "Úsáid sonraí oscailte Wikimedia"

#: use-content/data.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Access publicly-available, open-licensed data about Wikimedia projects, including bulk downloads, streams of recent changes, and page statistics."
msgstr "Rochtain a fháil ar shonraí atá ar fáil go poiblí agus faoi cheadúnas oscailte faoi thionscadail Wikimedia, lena n-áirítear íoslódálacha mórchóir, sruthanna athruithe le déanaí, agus staitisticí leathanaigh."

#: use-content/data.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Research:Data)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Meta-Wiki]( https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Research:Data)"

#: use-content/data.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Explore structured data with Wikidata"
msgstr "Iniúchadh a dhéanamh ar shonraí struchtúrtha le Wikidata"

#: use-content/data.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikidata is a free and open knowledge base that can be read and edited by both humans and machines. Learn how to access data from Wikidata, and follow best practices for reusing it."
msgstr "Is bunachar eolais saor in aisce agus oscailte é Wikidata ar féidir le daoine agus le meaisíní araon é a léamh agus a chur in eagar. Foghlaim conas rochtain a fháil ar shonraí ó Wikidata, agus lean na cleachtais is fearr chun iad a athúsáid."

#: use-content/data.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikidata](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Data_access)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Wikidata](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Data_access)"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:meta.title use-content/featured-apps.md:title
#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Explore featured apps"
msgstr "Iniúchadh aipeanna le feiceáil"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "App gallery"
msgstr "Gailearaí aipeanna"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Browse example apps that demonstrate best practices for using Wikimedia APIs, including fetching wiki content, logging in, and editing pages."
msgstr "Brabhsáil samplaí d’aipeanna a léiríonn dea-chleachtais maidir le húsáid APIanna Wikimedia, lena n-áirítear ábhar vicí a fháil, logáil isteach agus leathanaigh a chur in eagar."

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit the gallery](https://apps-gallery.toolforge.org)"
msgstr "[Tabhair cuairt ar an ngailearaí](https://apps-gallery.toolforge.org)"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Wikipedia visualizations"
msgstr "Amharcléirithe Vicipéid"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "“See, also” is a gallery of apps that visualize data from Wikipedia. Check out the gallery to get inspired and learn about available data and APIs."
msgstr "Is gailearaí d’aipeanna é “Féach freisin” a léiríonn sonraí ó Vicipéid. Féach ar an ngailearaí chun inspioráid a fháil agus foghlaim faoi shonraí agus APIanna atá ar fáil."

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit the gallery](https://seealso.org/)"
msgstr "[Tabhair cuairt ar an ngailearaí](https://seeelso.org/)"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Wikidata visualizations"
msgstr "Amharcléirithe Wikidata"

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikidata is a machine-readable knowledge base with millions of items. Browse this list of visualizations to get inspired and see open source examples of how to reuse Wikidata."
msgstr "Is bunachar eolais inléite ag meaisín é Wikidata ina bhfuil na milliúin míreanna. Brabhsáil an liosta seo d’amharcléirithe chun inspioráid a fháil agus samplaí foinse oscailte a fheiceáil ar conas Wikidata a athúsáid."

#: use-content/featured-apps.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikidata](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Tools/Visualize_data)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar Wikidata](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Tools/Visualize_data)"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Display information from Wikidata"
msgstr "Taispeáin faisnéis ó Wikidata"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Use the MediaWiki API to fetch and display information from Wikidata. Learn how Wikipedia articles are associated with Wikidata and how to parse Wikidata structures."
msgstr "Bain úsáid as API MediaWiki chun faisnéis a fháil agus a thaispeáint ó Wikidata. Foghlaim conas a bhaineann ailt Vicipéid le Wikidata agus conas struchtúir Wikidata a pharsáil."

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Presenting_Wikidata_knowledge)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org]( https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Presenting_Wikidata_knowledge)"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Display the picture of the day"
msgstr "Taispeáin pictiúr an lae"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to use the MediaWiki API to fetch the daily featured picture from Wikipedia. This tutorial uses Python and the Flask framework."
msgstr "Foghlaim conas API MediaWiki a úsáid chun an pictiúr laethúil a fháil ó Vicipéid. Úsáideann an rang teagaisc seo Python agus creatlach Flask."

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Picture_of_the_day_viewer)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Pictiúr_an_lae_amharcóir)"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 15 (header)
msgid "Get started querying Wikidata"
msgstr "Tosaigh ag fiosrú Wikidata"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 16 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to query Wikidata with SPARQL. This tutorial covers the basics of Wikidata and how to use the Wikidata Query Service."
msgstr "Foghlaim conas fiosrúcháin a dhéanamh ar Wikidata le SPARQL. Clúdaíonn an rang teagaisc seo bunghnéithe Wikidata agus conas Seirbhís Fiosrúcháin Wikidata a úsáid."

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more](https://wdqs-tutorial.toolforge.org)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh](https://wdqs-tutorial.toolforge.org)"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 18 (header)
msgid "Search articles by location"
msgstr "Cuardaigh ailt de réir suímh"

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 19 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to use the MediaWiki API to search for Wikipedia articles near a specific location. This tutorial uses JavaScript, Python, and the Flask framework."
msgstr "Foghlaim conas API MediaWiki a úsáid chun ailt Vicipéide a chuardach in aice le suíomh ar leith. Úsáideann an rang teagaisc seo JavaScript, Python, agus creatlach Flask."

#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 20 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Nearby_places_viewer)"
msgstr "[Léigh tuilleadh ar mediawiki.org]( https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Nearby_places_viewer)"

